FBIS3-38555 "drweu024__a94031" FBIS-WEU-94-024-A Document Type:Daily Report 4 February 1994 ANNEX Germany Laermann Nominated To Replace Ortleb AU0402111494 Hamburg DPA in German 1014 GMT 4 Feb 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU0402111494 Hamburg DPA Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Bonn -- Following a vote in the Federal Executive Committee and the Bundestag group of the Free Democratic Party of Germany [FDP], Karl-Hans Laermann has been appointed the new federal education minister. University Professor Laermann, 64, is the research policy spokesman for the FDP Bundestag group.
